articles.title: Stoinis Out, Ellis In As Cricket Australia Announce 2024/25 Men's Contract List | Cricket News Today - Wisden
articles.description: Cricket Australia have announced their contract list for 23 male cricketers for the 2024/25 season. They come into effect from July 1, 2024.
